---
source: crates/ridge-lexer/tests/snapshots.rs
expression: render(LOG_ANALYZER)
---
0..362 DOC_COMMENT "Reads a log file whose lines follow the format \"YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS LEVEL message\",\nparses each line into a LogEntry record, filters by a minimum severity level supplied\nvia argv, groups the surviving entries by hour-of-day (0–23), and prints a text\nhistogram to stdout.  All I/O happens at the edges; inner parsing and aggregation\nfunctions are pure."
